end experience, but can cobble together a simple site with a static site generator. (I have used eleventy for my band's website.)\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"My wife doesn't want to put her artwork online as she does not want it to be used to train LLMs. I wonder if this has culminated in any libraries that makes it feasible for me to build her a custom site where the artwork is processed to defeat LLM training. I don't have a lot of front-end experience, but can cobble together a simple site with a static site generator. (I have used eleventy for my band's website.)","submitter_user":"stig","user_is_author":true,"tags":["ask","programming","vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/lbjdlo","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/lbjdlo/what_s_advice_for_llm_poisoning_artwork"},{"short_id":"xhplww","created_at":"2026-06-21T13:53:58.000-05:00","title":"Optimizing #[sqlx::test] rebuild time","url":"https://kobzol.github.io/rust/2026/06/21/optimizing-sqlx-test-rebuild-time.html","score":16,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"ohrv","user_is_author":false,"tags":["performance","rust"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/xhplww","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/xhplww/optimizing_sqlx_test_rebuild_time"},{"short_id":"ontg5a","created_at":"2026-06-21T13:35:18.000-05:00","title":"AmigaOS 2: the greatest upgrade","url":"https://www.datagubbe.se/os20up/","score":18,"flags":0,"comment_count":2,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"classichasclass","user_is_author":false,"tags":["retrocomputing"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ontg5a","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ontg5a/amigaos_2_greatest_upgrade"},{"short_id":"dus74u","created_at":"2026-06-21T12:01:59.000-05:00","title":"Remote work increases social isolation","url":"https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.aec7671","score":8,"flags":2,"comment_count":15,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"apromixately","us